      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents. The interior shows significant signs of use, including some stains and wear on the upholstery. All major mechanical systems are functional, though the vehicle may require some maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
