    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an accessible price point. While the engine and transmission are functional, please be aware that the body shows some cosmetic blemishes, including several paint chips and a small dent on the rear fender. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and some staining consistent with its age. Mechanically, the car is reliable for daily use, though it will eventually require attention for a minor suspension creak and an aging battery. It is a honest, high-mileage driver that gets the job done.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
